Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.99,0:02:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,請進 請自便
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.71,0:02:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,建得真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.18,0:03:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,稍加收拾一下就能住了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,真的可以借給我們嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.30,0:03:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.93,0:03:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,這個 蘋果 屋 只在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.07,0:03:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,收穫季節使用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.44,0:03:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,有藥師能蒞臨此地 大家也都很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.88,0:03:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟這城裡沒多少醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.01,0:03:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,要有什麼需要 請跟我說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.22,0:03:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.31,0:03:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.14,0:03:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不不 不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.44,0:03:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嗚…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.98,0:03:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.16,0:03:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,暫時就以這裡為據點活動了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,薇爾貝爾也一起住多好…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,請不必擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是隨風而行隨心所向
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.25,0:03:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,自由自在的漫遊者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.21,0:03:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是你們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.59,0:03:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪麗恩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.01,0:03:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,看到琳卡的時候就知道妳也在了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,中央的精英在這種邊境幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.37,0:03:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,因為種種原因
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.89,0:04:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,現在成了這裡的開發班班長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.51,0:04:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那妳是那兩個孩子的上司？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪麗恩 妳有我姐姐的消息嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是什麼事情都行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,妮歐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就算我知道也不能告訴妳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.96,0:04:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,想想妳我的立場
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.74,0:04:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,還是一如既往的死腦筋啊妳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.51,0:04:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,本來也該向中央報告你們的事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這次也算你們救了他們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.54,0:04:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我就當不知道好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.60,0:04:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪麗恩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但是可別在城裡惹是生非
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.05,0:04:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,特別是薇爾貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,再會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.86,0:04:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我也在以我的方式找著她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,妮歐 薇爾貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才那不是我們的班長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我們認識的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,以前打過些交道…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.69,0:05:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 沒跟妳說過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.61,0:05:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那個天然加白癡的劍士當然也認識
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.27,0:05:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,琳卡也認識的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.89,0:05:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,說得真難聽…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,阿嚏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.45,0:05:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,對了對了 聽克羅娜說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.89,0:05:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,妮歐妳要住在這兒是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.87,0:05:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 暫時住一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,要開間藥店
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 開在這種庫房裡行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.32,0:05:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我們來裝修一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,既然要幹就來大幹一場
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.32,0:05:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,放這裡可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,桶兒！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 這個是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.93,0:06:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,哇…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,還有感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,有…有的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.02,0:06:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.14,0:06:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我也一直很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,只是個裝飾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,可是能動 還有感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是用煉金術做成的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是羅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.18,0:06:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,這是小時候媽媽給我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.72,0:06:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,妳媽媽也是煉金術士嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然該說曾經是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我還很小的時候就因為瘟疫去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,老實說我也不太記得我媽媽的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.72,0:06:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,學到的煉金術卻還記得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,愛絲卡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.19,0:06:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我本以為妳只是個輕飄飄的傻姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到還有著很沉重的往事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 突然覺得剛才被損得很慘…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.76,0:07:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧 稍微拿出點幹勁來就能做成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,薇爾貝爾妳好像什麼都沒做…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.12,0:07:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來該準備房間裡的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.98,0:07:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,需要些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,床 桌子 椅子？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,小裝飾是需要品味的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.56,0:07:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,就由我和妮歐來準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.43,0:07:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,二位去準備家具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.91,0:07:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.14,0:07:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 品味？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,桌子要折疊的就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.08,0:07:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 儘量…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.32,0:07:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…大桌子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,一個人住用得著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是配藥需要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,家具要在哪兒買呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.11,0:07:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂 正朝這邊過來的二位煉金術士
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,還有這位打扮可疑的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 卡朵拉 妳好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.81,0:07:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,妳說誰可疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.20,0:07:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 這可說錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.48,0:08:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是打扮可疑的漂亮姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這還差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.76,0:08:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,這就行了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.30,0:08:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 卡朵拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.87,0:08:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.51,0:08:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,店裡賣家具嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.91,0:08:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不不 怎麼看都只賣些雜貨和小東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,當然有售
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,只要客人需要 不管什麼東西都能為您準備
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.30,0:08:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.99,0:08:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 愛絲卡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙可是老奸巨滑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定要大敲一筆中介費
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.58,0:08:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 不好意思但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想要這樣的尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.08,0:08:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 那是姐姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我要 我要 我要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.11,0:08:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 別鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.80,0:08:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我要 我要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.49,0:08:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.59,0:08:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 這條尾巴果然很引人注目
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,小孩子就更加是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是 這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:09:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,煉金術士姐姐 這條尾巴可以賣給小店嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.95,0:09:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.69,0:09:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,這個可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,要多少錢才賣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.97,0:09:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我願意高價收購
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,所以不是價錢的問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,高價大概是多高？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,賣掉也不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.65,0:09:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,薇…薇爾貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,妳怎麼也被說動了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.63,0:09:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對不賣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.01,0:09:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這是媽媽留下的珍貴的遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.15,0:09:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,既然是飽含回憶的東西那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.53,0:09:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,做出這個的媽媽也已經不在了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.64,0:09:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是用煉金術做出來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,再用一樣方法做出來不就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.57,0:09:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,理論上是可行的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就是！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,柯爾賽特主要的收入源
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.33,0:09:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是特產 蘋果的銷售
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 蘋果一年只收穫一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.87,0:10:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,在這之外就只能靠小商小販勉強度日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣經濟也當然不景氣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但要是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,能把這種嶄新的裝飾品大量生產
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,銷售到中央去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.19,0:10:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,說不定能掀起一時潮流
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,帶動地區經濟發展
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,受經濟制約的種種問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,也就能一舉得以解決
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.37,0:10:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,能這麼順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 也不是不可能的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,羅 羅吉你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.59,0:10:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,煉金術不是牟利的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.99,0:10:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是為了大家的幸福而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.67,0:10:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不不 這也是為了大家的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.39,0:10:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,總之現在是要買桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 羅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:56.00,Title,,0,0,0,,{\an1\move(200,378,26,378)\1c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fad(200,0)\blur7.5\bord3\t(0,920,2,\blur0\bord0\1c&HD8F7F7&)}妮歐•阿爾圖爾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,熱火朝天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.35,0:11:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此 這兒應該能買得到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.51,0:11:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是愛絲卡嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.69,0:11:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,喲 愛絲卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.97,0:11:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我打算給起降場換幾塊地板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.51,0:11:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你們呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.97,0:11:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,裝蘋果的桶嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 今天是來買家具的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,家具？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.24,0:11:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,床 桌子和… 啊 椅子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼愛絲卡 妳要和那個小夥成家嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.86,0:11:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是幫別人的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.49,0:11:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼啊 別嚇我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.11,0:11:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,真是 怎麼連哥哥你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 要什麼樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.33,0:11:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 也是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣的不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不行的啦 羅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,多為妮歐的想法考慮考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.26,0:12:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.01,0:12:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不是很清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.27,0:12:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,也可以訂做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,只要妳開口 什麼都能給妳做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.91,0:12:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼都行？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟 我們是吃這口飯的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.63,0:12:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然不會煉金術
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.28,0:12:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但我們有從小就使著的這些工具
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.63,0:12:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,和這一身本事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.59,0:12:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不管什麼都能做給妳看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.59,0:12:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,畫個大概就好了 妳畫畫看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.80,0:12:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,這…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.93,0:12:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.51,0:12:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,居然三天就能做好 真不簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.15,0:12:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我再次體會到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.09,0:12:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是工匠還是煉金術士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.86,0:12:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,傳承技術 精進手藝這點都是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.53,0:13:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 羅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.29,0:13:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我 想試試
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,煉出這個尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.59,0:13:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,您肯為我做嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.59,0:13:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然沒什麼自信 不過我先試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.87,0:13:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託妳了～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,耶～耶～耶～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼突然就想做了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,這個尾巴…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.33,0:13:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是媽媽在病中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,為了讓我不會寂寞而做的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.38,0:13:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,做的時候我也一起幫忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是媽媽教我 煉金術的基礎的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.24,0:13:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 聽妳說過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.87,0:13:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,羅吉你也說過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,明明都不記得媽媽了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,卻還記得煉金術 好奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.82,0:13:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,學到的手藝是很難忘掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,要是做出來了一樣的尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.01,0:14:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信就能想起更多媽媽的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.17,0:14:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,哪兒都沒寫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟會動的尾巴什麼的 聽都沒聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.15,0:14:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,更別說還是有感覺的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.74,0:14:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,克羅娜的話應該知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.31,0:14:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,尾巴 的 配方嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道留下來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,米莉亞生前 不是那種
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,會把事情記下來的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.27,0:14:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,因為大而化之的個性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.19,0:14:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,也是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.61,0:14:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,雖說如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,也不是一點都沒記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.75,0:14:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.22,0:14:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是全部資料了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我找找看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.63,0:14:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.57,0:14:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,跟煉金術有關係的幾乎一點也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.94,0:14:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.45,0:15:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.91,0:15:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這本畫冊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,蜂鳥公主的…大冒險
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.74,0:15:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 小時候經常讓克羅娜講給我聽的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.72,0:15:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.12,0:15:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是 找東西的時候最要不得的節奏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.50,0:15:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,想…起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.32,0:15:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,對呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那時候的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,憑著回憶搜集起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.14,0:15:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,跟做菜似的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,總之先做著試試
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.31,0:16:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,做是做出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,卻動不了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.81,0:16:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,只是個形似神不似的小飾品而已呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.65,0:16:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:17:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道是技術不過關還是缺了點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.67,0:17:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,方向大概沒錯就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,成立卡朵拉公司的夢想…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.26,0:17:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,真遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,果然想的是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.47,0:17:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,該動的東西不動的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.89,0:17:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就只有強行讓它動了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,司掌物質的精靈喲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.69,0:17:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,羅吉 那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.14,0:17:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,卡朵拉 躲開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,妳說得輕巧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,在吵什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,別逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.07,0:17:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,欸 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪麗恩 退後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.03,0:17:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,琳卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,這 這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.66,0:17:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,薇爾貝爾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.62,0:17:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,妳到底做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.06,0:17:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我…不…不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.89,0:18:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.93,0:18:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.12,0:18:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪麗恩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.40,0:18:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,班長？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.38,0:18:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,唉呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.72,0:18:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,把動物的靈寄宿上去了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,請 請做點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,愛絲卡！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.77,0:18:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,連薇爾貝爾都
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這個 從另一個角度看 會好賣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,當心！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.65,0:18:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.51,0:18:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,別過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.30,0:18:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.80,0:19:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,抓到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.17,0:19:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.71,0:19:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,羅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,別鬆手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我這就去找…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.84,0:19:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,能把它塞進去的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我還在想怎麼支部裡一個人都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.14,0:19:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,這是在 幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.22,0:19:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,已經…抓不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.54,0:19:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,索爾！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.24,0:19:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,危險！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.15,0:19:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,愛絲卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.18,0:19:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,羅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.42,0:19:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,在開什麼會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.24,0:19:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,看起來玩得挺開心嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,支部長…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,現在不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,當心！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.67,0:19:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.55,0:19:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這是 怎麼回事 啊那裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,完蛋了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我都說了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.35,0:20:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,別給我惹是生非
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 妳們…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,果然我也要跟著挨駡…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,嗚 除了報告還要寫檢討了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.91,0:20:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦 大家也都笑著原諒妳了 不挺好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,雖說如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.08,0:20:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.17,0:20:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,在薇爾貝爾的魔法消失之後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.40,0:20:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,馬上就不能動了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.63,0:20:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,看來還是比不上媽媽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.34,0:20:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,到底還差點什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,說不定 是「對愛絲卡的愛」這種呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.71,0:20:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,為了不讓女兒 在自己生病照顧不到的時候寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.99,0:21:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但願這次烤得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.40,0:21:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.80,0:21:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.54,0:21:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,確實 雖然還是比不上我做的點心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.27,0:21:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,薇爾貝爾 妳會做點心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,當然會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.13,0:21:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,魔女的點心 當然好吃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.57,0:21:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.63,0:21:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,欸 妳真的不知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.48,0:21:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,要個大桌子的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.28,0:21:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,原來是這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.25,0:21:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,多虧二位了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.54,0:21:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝二位專程買來的桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.95,0:21:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,下次能做點點心給我嚐嚐嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.84,0:21:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不能白做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.50,0:21:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.70,0:21:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼不行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.31,0:23:33.67,Default,,0,0,12,,我當上前輩了！
